{"tid":647990,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【復仇者聯盟3】結局太驚嚇觀眾要心理輔導？有人激動暈倒送院","createTime":"2018-04-30T09:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T10:22:43.000Z","uid":66923,"like":79,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c4bf62bf0c5ea3bc27e2e360ceafa9225e0ecf","tid":647990,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:56:48.000Z","msg":"【復仇者聯盟3】結局太驚嚇觀眾要心理輔導？　有人激動暈倒送院<br />\n<br />\nMarvel十年大作《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》（Avengers: Infinity War，下稱《復仇者3》）已上映數日，未知各位觀眾入場睇戲未？對電影結局又有何感想？美國有不少觀眾看完《復仇者3》十分激動，不單有人話要接受心理輔導，更有觀眾散場時暈倒送院。<br />\n<br />\n美國比香港遲兩日才上映《復仇者3》，觀眾看過電影後紛紛於社交網站分享感想，雖然絕大部分都好守規矩沒劇透，但幾乎所有人都對結局表示震驚，以下節錄的反應相當有趣：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/175239_b019c309cca8ec848e3b489143db1f05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F175239_b019c309cca8ec848e3b489143db1f05.jpg&h=861e756f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「有冇《復仇者3》嘅心理輔導小組&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/175318_e4239ebc839a67c415687a8fa5f85fbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F175318_e4239ebc839a67c415687a8fa5f85fbc.jpg&h=a78dc289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我睇到3分1套戲開始喊，喊到完場，個人好似被挖空咗，我行唔到直線同諗唔到嘢」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/175343_49ee3c962c11a1511ecb40d90a66d8d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F175343_49ee3c962c11a1511ecb40d90a66d8d6.jpg&h=cf687e1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「當《復仇者3》散場之後，全部人幾乎寂靜咁行出去，消化吓剛剛睇咗啲咩，我第一次見到咁嘅場面，永遠都唔會忘記」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/175410_53ef26d9de1c5809b21cba94a26d455a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F175410_53ef26d9de1c5809b21cba94a26d455a.jpg&h=1fdb296e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我起身之後，精神上仍然唔OK，返到屋企仲諗緊琴晚套戲發生咩事，我嘔咗&hellip;我好耐未試過傷心到嘔。天呀，點會有家長覺得帶仔女去睇呢套戲係好事，佢哋會有創傷」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/175437_b5df8be07343c9135cdc13dfeab7af8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F175437_b5df8be07343c9135cdc13dfeab7af8e.jpg&h=46b4ca16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「成套戲我最鍾意嗰Part係，當完場時有人大叫『乜X嘢』，成個戲院都有回音」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/175509_47d42a7067530e802aaca136831a81a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F175509_47d42a7067530e802aaca136831a81a9.jpg&h=85a14d25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「你哋有冇試過心碎？去到一個程度係喊唔出，咩都感覺唔到，唔想食飯、講嘢、同埋做任何嘢？《復仇者3》會令你變成咁」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/175526_9741ffb2d26eba1544d3bd2d5e309496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F175526_9741ffb2d26eba1544d3bd2d5e309496.jpg&h=376e062f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民拍下有觀眾睇完《復仇者3》暈倒被送院一刻。（網上圖片）"},{"pid":"d44cdb8be59bf34f32fd48b7e4fbff3fee001f3a","tid":647990,"uid":11962,"like":9,"dislike":53,"score":-44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:57:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾到嚇撚暈？"},{"pid":"6c77c6dc54c35ad3f3ed72dc183eee7accbe4824","tid":647990,"uid":24788,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T09:59:57.000Z","msg":"On9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28eb675df31ebc0e3b4f72647acf6eba065e4d9","tid":647990,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T10:01:28.000Z","msg":"好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過將來打WW3全球死三分一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到時D人會咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9156e7226f7b86a353135ff481d6246a0337db","tid":647990